:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"誠哥使撚我地保護咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a793b9ccfc1530eadf460c6f8495a9c2428f333","tid":1477162,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:15:03.000Z","msg":"月供1,6,1038，無供錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d74d6d834f5087af4c8e1e41128dae764af0335","tid":1477162,"uid":292424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:18:19.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n因果由國 容港治己<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bc7e72d012815cff0d751963b2ef276559737d","tid":1477162,"uid":38568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:23:08.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"eb2b4e48384c6b939e320cad200dece5fad4623f","tid":1477162,"uid":280582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:26:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">誠哥教抗爭</span></strong></span><br />\n01訪問誠哥，入面有兩句「應以何身得度者，即現何身而為之說法」。意思即係話，係會唔同人有唔同解讀，你以自己身份去解讀就最正確。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用示威者身份解讀<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">停止暴力</span> -</strong> 誠哥和理非 （但佢唔可以開口撐勇武，所以大家跟住終極行動守則繼續做就得,仲有唔好唔記得，終極行動守則係琴晚出，仲要講明係律師歷史學家寫嘅，背後必有重量級精英出手寫，啱啱係誠哥廣告率先係連登漏夜曝光前幾小時出）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">堅持法治</span></strong> - 香港出咗法治問題<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">愛自己</span></strong> - 不送頭<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一國兩制</span></strong> - 五大訴求在一國兩制框架下合理訴求，無人要港獨<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">謙和而珍之</span></strong> - be humble, 珍惜民意<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">投放資源在青年工作，永不後悔，因為投資青年，就是投資未來</span></strong> - 打林鄭塊面（they have no stake in society which so many people have helped to build)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不要讓今天的激情，成為明天的遺憾</span></strong>- 要小心行事，唔好變64<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報導再講<br />\n至於李嘉誠次子李澤楷旗下的盈科拓展集團及富衛保險，亦在《東方日報》刊登廣告，內容為「反對暴力行為 維護社會秩序 恢復理性討論」。<br />\n- 繼續和理非<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hko1.com/article/364457\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko1.com%2Farticle%2F364457&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjalxR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=973b9064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hko1.com/article/364457</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再睇埋01呢個星期創辦人于品海寫嘅-開到口叫繼續和理非合法參與社會運動。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/363800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F363800&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjalxR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=5aa60968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/363800</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［勇武和理非大和解］終極行動守則上線了<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1474951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1474951</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因果由國 容港治己</span></span><br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEV19aT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEV19aT.png&h=ae1ccc94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7fd3dff2544765c278bdb2b6e572e3043945b938","tid":1477162,"uid":63635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"佢使撚你地保護咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0deabff736429ee49e67ecd5bb9ef18e415c1dec","tid":1477162,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:33:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f230a27b4a382be33e0a35b2a1b2ac354adae18","tid":1477162,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:34:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>因果由國，容港治己<br />\n